        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6330",
        "content": "It would be interesting to figure out just how many foot pounds of energy men have saved themselves, since the creation of the world, by keeping up the pretense that a special knack is required for washing dishes and for dusting, and that the knack is wholly feminine.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
