        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6330",
        "content": "Like children in a toy shop, we have chosen to live with the most amusing of talking and walking dolls, without ever attempting to tear down the sign which says, \"Do not touch.\" In fact we have helped to set it in place. That is a pity.",
